{"tid":2056612,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"點解咁大件事到而家都仲未有人講？？","createTime":"2020-06-08T23:04:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-08T23:46:04.000Z","uid":343629,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"5368d07ba297b318647600fcaf2d3586d406f0f8","tid":2056612,"uid":343629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T23:04:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5GpECtU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5GpECtU.jpg&h=fc64ee73&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n係吖就係今日都冇人提<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n6.9香港人抗爭一周年港島區大遊行<br />\n<br />\nDresscode：非黑衫 <br />\n集合時間：18:30 <br />\n因為朝早晏晝，市民要返工，呢個時間可以俾收工人士參與 <br />\n <br />\n17:30公佈邊區集合，18:00公佈詳細集合地點，18:30公佈路綫，請留意以上兩個channel。 <br />\n請手足提早到達stand by，早到可以喺附近扮吓港豬，然後6點半一齊出現<br />\n<br />\n#Q&amp;A<br />\nQ: 點解嗰日dresscode係非黑衫？<br />\n<br />\nA:<br />\n非黑衫，姐係彩虹戰衣<br />\n<br />\n524，527，行動嘅人多數都係非黑衫。<br />\n<br />\n一年前69嘅dresscode唔係黑衫，而係白衫，但如果公開講嗰日着白衫，咁d狗嘅ss對象由黑衫轉移到白衫，所以講嗰日着非黑衫。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nQ: 冇黑衫，勇武點做野？<br />\nA: 勇武會自發行動，識帶衫，識換衫，識着衫。佢地可因應情況選擇着黑衫或非黑衫。<br />\n<br />\nTg:<a href=\"https://t.me/revenuetower87\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Frevenuetower87&d=N73AYdKZ8ITSJgwUZ5%2B19tLD3cQOkzCKckuFp%2FmPVdU%3D&h=d9f28657\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/revenuetower87</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔講咁多到時見<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><em>光復香港！時代革命！</em></strong></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><em>民眾自強！香港獨立！</em></strong></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><em>香港獨立！唯一出路</em></strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"5588ffc7b227a7781964d561f51e943554f38576","tid":2056612,"uid":33874,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T23:06:23.000Z","ms